<main id="page-main">
  <header id="page-main-header" class="jumbotron splash">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Discover your team, mentor, project, or cause.</h2>
      <h1>Find your change.</h1>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="container col-xs-12 text-center">
    <h3>What does our platform do?</h3>
    <h2>Connects:</h2>

    <section class="col-xs-4">
      <h3>Individuals to Individuals</h3>
      <%= image_tag("indiv_to_indiv.png", alt: "Individuals to individuals",
                                          class: "center-block") %>
      <p>A high school student passionate about biology can study genetic mutations with a researcher at a local university.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="col-xs-4">
      <h3>Individuals to Groups</h3>
      <%= image_tag("indiv_to_group.png", alt: "Individuals to groups",
                                          class: "center-block") %>
      <p>An engineer can design and build sustainable chairs for a children's school in Zimbabwe.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="col-xs-4">
      <h3>Groups to Groups</h3>
      <%= image_tag("group_to_group.png", alt: "Groups to groups",
                                          class: "center-block") %>
      <p>A city government in India can improve the health of its local produce by working with an organic pesticides startup company.</p>
    </section>

    <h2>GET STARTED</h2>
    <h4>Sign up for blog and milestone updates!</h4>
  </section>

  <section class="container col-xs-12">
    <form class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="name">Name</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="email">Email</label>
        <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label>What are you interested in?</label>
        <div class="checkbox">
          <label><input type="checkbox" name="global" />Global Development</label>
        </div>
        <div class="checkbox">
          <label><input type="checkbox" name="tech" />Technology Development</label>
        </div>
        <div class="checkbox">
          <label><input type="checkbox" name="research" />Research</label>
        </div>
        <div class="checkbox">
          <label><input type="checkbox" name="club" />Volunteer/Club Opportunities</label>
        </div>
        <div class="checkbox">
          <label><input type="checkbox" name="learn" />Learning Opportunities</label>
        </div>
        <div class="checkbox">
          <label><input type="checkbox" name="job" />Job Openings</label>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success center-block">Subscribe</button>
    </form>

    <section class="col-xs-6 text-center">
      <%= link_to "Post Opportunities", post_path, class: "btn btn-default" %>
    </section>
    <section class="col-xs-6 text-center">
      <%= link_to "Browse Opportunities", root_path, class: "btn btn-default" %>
    </section>
  </section>
</main>
